summary: West-MEC prepares students for career success by providing opportunities to grow their knowledge through further education and skill development. We span 3,600+ square miles representing 46 high schools across the West Valley. Our students have the choice to participate in tuition free programs(ex. Cosmetology, Medical Assisting, Coding, Auto Tech, etc.) focused on hands-on instruction, leadership development training and industry certification.West-MEC also offers Adult Education in similar pathways and Professional Development offerings for educators, administrators and business leaders.
